<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>中英文圣经</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p { margin: 0.6rem 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px; padding: 12px 24px; background: #0066cc; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 500; }
    .btn:hover { background: #0052a3; }
    a { color: #0066cc; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>中英文圣经</h1>
  <p>「中英文圣经」支持中英对照读经、多版本阅读。点击下方按钮获取应用。</p>
  <p><a href="#" id="storeBtn" class="btn">获取应用</a></p>
  <script>
    (function() {
      var ua = navigator.userAgent || navigator.vendor || window.opera;
      var isIOS = /iPad|iPhone|iPod/.test(ua) || (navigator.platform === 'MacIntel' && navigator.maxTouchPoints > 1);
      var isAndroid = /android/i.test(ua);
      var appStore = 'https://apps.apple.com/app/id1128667810';
      var playStore = 'https://play.google.com/apps/test/com.tianyue.holybible/2';
      var btn = document.getElementById('storeBtn');
      var url = isIOS ? appStore : (isAndroid ? playStore : playStore);
      btn.href = url;
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
